				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/dearlove" rel="tag">Dearlove</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/machon" rel="tag">Machon</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/manningham-buller" rel="tag">Manningham-Buller</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/mi5" rel="tag">MI5</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/mi6" rel="tag">MI6</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/rimington" rel="tag">Rimington</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/spies-2" rel="tag">spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/war" rel="tag">war</a>			</span>
						
